snippet: Stan Wawrinka outslugged Japanese sixth seed Kei Nishikori 4-6 7-5 6-4 6-2 in energy-sapping humidity at Flushing Meadows on Friday to set up a U.S. Open final against world number one Novak Djokovic....
lead_paragraph: Stan Wawrinka outslugged Japanese sixth seed Kei Nishikori 4-6 7-5 6-4 6-2 in energy-sapping humidity at Flushing Meadows on Friday to set up a U.S. Open final against world number one Novak Djokovic.

headline.print_headline: Wawrinka Tops Nishikori to Reach Final Versus Djokovic
headline.main: Wawrinka Tops Nishikori to Reach Final Versus Djokovic
